race.description: Golden Beach Ss P&C Hcp Maiden
race.comment: HE'SGOTTHESAY (1) returned in good order with a solid second at Eagle Farm and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Has placed around this circuit and should find this a touch easier than that first-up effort. Rates the testing material. TULONG (3) strips fitter second-up from the spell and gets the services of Maloney in the irons. Looms as the main danger in this line-up. Former Victorian ZEDIQUETTE (8) just ran into one better when having the first run for the new stable and Thompson sticks in the saddle. Include in calculations. PARISIENNE PIPER (7) best of the rest with the 2kg claim.
